snippet.title: Resident Evil Village: Gold Edition - Official Mercenaries Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for Resident Evil Village: Gold Edition, which includes the base game, a new  Third Person Mode, The Mercenaries, as well as Shadows of Rose-- which follows the story of Ethan’s daughter, Rosemary.

#IGN #ResidentEvil
